videos.description: 1H (18:54) UNM Cullen Neal made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Cullen Neal comes off a screen and drains another three early in the first half

videos.description: 1H (17:39) AUB T.J. Dunans made Dunk.
videos.headline: Kareem Canty skips it ahead to T.J. Dunans who finises with a dunk

videos.description: 1H (15:03) UNM Cullen Neal made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Cullen Neal hits his third three-pointer, all within the first five minutes of play

videos.description: Tyler Harris misses the shot but Cinmeon Bowers is there to clean it up with the powerful, putback dunk to put Auburn up 22-19 on New Mexico.
videos.headline: Bowers attacks the glass with powerful putback

videos.description: 1H (9:22) UNM New Mexico  Turnover.
videos.headline: Craig Neal wants the New Mexico shot clock violation reviewed

videos.description: 1H (8:08) UNM Elijah Brown made Layup.
videos.headline: Elijah Brown goes coast to coast, weaves through traffic for a layup

videos.description: Kareem Canty knocks down a 3-pointer and celebrates with a "what time is it?!" celebration.
videos.headline: Canty knocks down the 3, lets everybody know what time it is
Tim Williams gets blocked from behind and hits the floor hard, gets up on his own power and comes out of the game

videos.description: 1H (2:03) AUB Foul on Cinmeon Bowers.
videos.headline: Cinmeon Bowers gets called going over the back, slams the ball in frustration and gets a technical, Bruce Pearl can't believe it

videos.description: 1H (1:04) AUB Bryce Brown made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by T.J. Dunans.
videos.headline: T.J. Dunans penetrates and kicks it out to Bryce Brown in the corner for three

videos.description: 1H (0:08) UNM Elijah Brown made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Elijah Brown hits the three point jumper, ends the first half with twenty points

videos.headline: Elijah Brown knocks down a contested three

videos.headline: Kareem Canty lobs one up to Jordan Granger for a two handed jam

videos.headline: Cullen Neal knocks down another three

videos.description: 2H (9:06) AUB Kareem Canty made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Kareem Canty hits a three from deep

videos.description: 2H (6:47) AUB T.J. Dunans made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Kareem Canty.
videos.headline: Kareem Canty dishes to T.J. Dunans for three

videos.description: 2H (4:39) AUB Cinmeon Bowers made Dunk. Assisted by TJ Lang.
videos.headline: T.J. Lang pitches ahead to Cinmeon Bowers for a dunk in transition

videos.description: 2H (2:16) UNM Elijah Brown made Jumper.
videos.headline: Elijah Brown makes a wild shot, his team can't believe it

videos.description: 2H (0:53) UNM Obij Aget made Dunk. Assisted by Cullen Neal.
videos.headline: Cullen Neal is a play maker, dishes to Obij Aget who finishes with an authoritative dunk

videos.description: 2H (0:28) AUB Kareem Canty made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Kareem Canty takes a step back and drains a clutch three late in the second

videos.description: In the final seconds of the game, Auburn's T.J. Dunans steals the ball, races down the court and lobs it up to Cinmeon Bowers for the empathic alley-oop to seal the victory for the Tigers.
videos.headline: That's how you finish a game off in style
